…<br></li><li>VGhlcmUgYXJlIG1vcmUgc2VjcmV0cyB0aGF0IG1vcnRhbHMgY2Fubm90IGtub3cgOik=</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648210/extras/f6b42f6dbc0de39a5a08ef4ca31dc95a.avif?t=1690456393\" width=516 height=288 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动画短片“Apopia：破碎的王冠”公开！</h2>在这段动画短片中一睹《Apopia：序章》前发生的种种故事，了解莫利被驱逐出城堡的背后缘由。<br>观看并提升你的试玩体验",
